quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  89,1,"Alla ceniiɗo O woondarii wenndoogo."
  89,2,"Alla woondirii jemmaaji sappa battandiiɗi e lewri jil hijjati."
  89,3,"Mi woondiri ko ɗimmita e ko teelɗi e geɗe goodaaɗe."
  89,4,"Mi woondiri jemma si mbo arii; mbo ɓenni mbo runtii, ma on njoɓe golle mon."
  89,5,"Mbela ina ndee woondoore ko jaɓnata jom hakkille?"
  89,6,"Mbela A yi*aani-aan nelaado- no Alla waɗi Aad en yimɓe Huud nde ɓe penni nelaaɓe?"
  89,7,"Leñol Aad ummingol e taani mum en Iram jom darnde."
  89,8,"Mbo hono mum tagaaka e dow leydi."
  89,9,"Mbela A yi*aani no joom Ma waɗi Samuud yimɓe Saalihu, ɓeen seekɓe pelle, ɓe mbaɗi ɗe cuujɗi."
  89,10,"Mbela A yi*aani hono joom ma waɗi Fir*awna oon jom penɗe ɗe o leptiratno yimɓe."
  89,11,"ɓee fof mbewiina njawti keeri e canndallaagal e tooñnnge, gooto e mum fof yawtiino keerol e leydi mum."
  89,12,"ɓe kebbini e hendi bonannde sabu ko ɓe caakti toon ko e keefeeru e goopi."
  89,13,"Alla meeɗniɓe lepte cattuɗe, O ɗoofiɓe e dow leydi."
  89,14,"joom Ma-aan nelaado- na tommbii golle mum en na ndaara ɗe, ngam yoɓde oon moƴƴinɗo aljanna, oon bonnuɗo yoɓee yiite."
  89,15,"Tawi ko aade na e neesu mum si joom makko jaribiimo mbo O teddini mbo; O neeminiri mbo ngalu e ɓesngu e koongu, o sikka wonde ɗuum ko teddungal ka Alla, o wiya:joom am teddinii kam sabu mina haandi e teddungal Makko."
  89,16,"Si tawii O jaribiimo mbo O faaɗni arsuko makko, o sikka ɗuum ko koyeere makko to joom mum, o wiya:joom am hoynii kam."
  89,17,"Alah wonah no aade mbaadinta wonde neemineede ko daliilu weluya Alla wonande maccuɗo mum, e wonde satteende ko maande koyeere to joomiraawo, ko woodi ko woni on teddintaana baaya e arsuko Alla okki mon o."
  89,18,"O hirjindirtah ñamminde baasɗo mbo alah nguura."
  89,19,"Hoɗon ñaama hakkeeli lohɓe rewɓe e yatimeeɓe ñaamgol cattungol ko aldah e reentaade na dagii wolla dagaaki."
  89,20,"Hoɗon njiɗi jawdi sanne, lomon nafkude ndi e laawol Alla sabu reerɗude e hendi."
  89,21,"Haanaani nde golle mon wa*ata nih, ciftare si leydi ndi dimmbaam dimmbere sattunde ndi yirbi."
  89,22,"joom ma ara-aan nelaado- ngam ñaawde hakkunde jiyaaɓe; malaykaaji ɗi ngara na mbaɗi saffeeji."
  89,23,"E oon ñalawma jahannama addee hombo waɗi 70000 ujunere ginol, kala heen gootol na e mum 70000 wuluure malayka na ndasa mbo, ndeen noon aade siftoro ko o welsandino, kono ko siftorde nafata oon ñalawma, o ñalngu ko mbo njoɓdi wonah mbo golle."